    {
      "para_id": "p10",
      "section_id": "s2",
      "section_path": [
        "Algorithmic Pluralism"
      ],
      "ordinal": 10,
      "text": "mental health content every 39 seconds which, even if not explicitly promoting eating disorders, can be damaging to teens' mental health.",
      "char_len": 137,
      "chunk_word_count": 21,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.9487179487179487,
        "digit": 0.017094017094017096,
        "non_space": 0.8540145985401459
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.5490384615384616,
        "flags": []
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "threshold+top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p11",
      "section_id": "s2",
      "section_path": [
        "Algorithmic Pluralism"
      ],
      "ordinal": 11,
      "text": "CCDH research investigating misleading claims about extreme weather events found that Alex Jones' posts spreading false information about the LA wildfires received 408 million views – more than the combined viewership of relevant posts from ten major news outlets and ten key emergency response organizations. Jones used his X account to promote claims that emergency responders were confiscating food and that the fires were a part of a globalist plot to deindustrialize America.",
      "char_len": 480,
      "chunk_word_count": 72,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.9828431372549019,
        "digit": 0.007352941176470588,
        "non_space": 0.85
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.9871323529411764,
        "flags": []
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "threshold+top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p12",
      "section_id": "s2",
      "section_path": [
        "Algorithmic Pluralism"
      ],
      "ordinal": 12,
      "text": "Recommender systems have also proved harmful on YouTube. CCDH analyzed recommendations made to a fictional 13-year-old teenage girl in Ireland, finding that 1 in 3 recommendations were for harmful eating disorder content and 3 in 4 were for content about eating disorders or weight loss. The content was not removed, age-restricted or labelled despite YouTube's claims that they do so in their DSA risk assessment.",
      "char_len": 414,
      "chunk_word_count": 66,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.9571428571428572,
        "digit": 0.017142857142857144,
        "non_space": 0.8454106280193237
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.967857142857143,
        "flags": []
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "threshold+top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p13",
      "section_id": "s2",
      "section_path": [
        "Algorithmic Pluralism"
      ],
      "ordinal": 13,
      "text": "In 2025 Meta disclosed that only 7% of Instagram user time was spent viewing content from friends, with the remainder dedicated to third-party content. This indicates a shift away from 'social' media towards something more akin to traditional media.",
      "char_len": 249,
      "chunk_word_count": 39,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.943127962085308,
        "digit": 0.023696682464454975,
        "non_space": 0.8473895582329317
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.819845971563981,
        "flags": []
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "threshold+top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p14",
      "section_id": "s2",
      "section_path": [
        "Algorithmic Pluralism"
      ],
      "ordinal": 14,
      "text": "In this shift, recommender systems assume the role of editor. But as a hyper-personalized window through which consumers are served media, recommender systems remain geared towards optimizing engagement rather than serving the best interests of users. Given this power, and its potential for misuse, the Digital Fairness Act must enhance users' ability to choose the media they consume through a right to constructive optimization.",
      "char_len": 431,
      "chunk_word_count": 64,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.9755434782608695,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.8538283062645011
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.9816576086956521,
        "flags": []
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "threshold+top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p15",
      "section_id": "s2",
      "section_path": [
        "Algorithmic Pluralism"
      ],
      "ordinal": 15,
      "text": "Constructive optimization can be operationalized in two ways:",
      "char_len": 61,
      "chunk_word_count": 8,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.9814814814814815,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.8852459016393442
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.43611111111111117,
        "flags": [
          "very_short"
        ]
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p16",
      "section_id": "s2",
      "section_path": [
        "Algorithmic Pluralism"
      ],
      "ordinal": 16,
      "text": "Users give VLOPs input into the design and operation of the recommender system.",
      "char_len": 79,
      "chunk_word_count": 13,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.9850746268656716,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.8481012658227848
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.4540837479270315,
        "flags": []
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p17",
      "section_id": "s2",
      "section_path": [
        "Algorithmic Pluralism"
      ],
      "ordinal": 17,
      "text": "Platforms should consider the views of individuals or communities when constructing the recommender system through an easy-to-use communication channel made available by the platform.",
      "char_len": 183,
      "chunk_word_count": 25,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.98125,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.8743169398907104
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.6345486111111112,
        "flags": []
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "threshold+top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
